Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.09,0:00:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的那个你看了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了 看了 真有趣 简直太扯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}（露出肚脐的造型藏有秘密）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}（心型吊坠是秘密道具）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟钝少女小秋… 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好 乃木坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个… 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香原来是徒步上学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为有专车接送呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦 学校离家这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 步行有利健康嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:00:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕 不可饶恕 不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人 你刚才用手机看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迟钝少女小秋的官网啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想了解下春香所喜欢的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是废柴少女小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称得上是小秋的宿敌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕 不可饶恕 不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总 总之我们先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:22.67,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,470)\fad(1000,1000)}『我还是第一次…』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}喂 找到了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}还没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起 我有点得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的爱好是秘密吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这是我和裕人之间的小秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 这个 这周日你有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能 能陪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能 能陪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能陪我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}（能和我交往吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这难道是约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我是想去买个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果愿陪我的话 就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事一般就叫“约会”吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人心里没底…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想如果被你拒绝了可怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你要去的地方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我想去秋叶原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶原 那里有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见 裕人 我还有好几家要逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 信长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有好多珍品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去路上小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 死也不再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶原这个鬼地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后 我就再没来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让你久等了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也刚刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶原站真是四通八达啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 裕人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你一直盯着看 我有点 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱 抱歉 我不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜花插在牛粪上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是演员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我们去买东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出发买东西咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是购物指南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指南？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我整理了今天的计划和目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了我整整三个小时哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先转这里 这里 和这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便去这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终目的地是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PDS？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便携游戏机Portable Dream Station的新型号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我梦寐以求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是小猫咪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫 是猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你看这只小猫咪怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这话有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我对这幅画还是蛮有信心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 画的蛮有冲击力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？ 哇 我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次拿给别人看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:06:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为春香做什么都很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她不擅长画画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟钝 迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？迟钝少女和废柴少女谁比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用先去买PDS吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果一上来就买掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的活动已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得出来买趟东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我想把最大的乐趣留到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是这里 虎之穴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 居然有这么多同人志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同人志？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样以动画或游戏为原型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由爱好者自己创作的漫画…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Animate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 居然有这么多周边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们去下一个站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你什么都不买么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 就在前面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可爱 太赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人 你看 好可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是看着这些可爱的东西 就觉得好幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么喜欢的话 买下不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也很想买
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但预算不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲很严格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用在兴趣上的零花钱很有限…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经攒好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜其所赐 小猪猪也上天堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能看看 我就很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 春香为什么会有这种兴趣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是五六年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挨了父亲的骂 跑去公园大哭了一场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 有个陌生男孩送了我一本书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本书难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 就是Innocent Smile的创刊号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我从没读过那种书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉间已经沉浸在了书里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把挨骂的痛苦都忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动漫真是美妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信长？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香 抱歉 打扰下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太稀奇了 裕人竟然会来秋叶原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于觉醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 说到底还不是因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 现在提那种事也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到秋叶原就该想到我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到我就该想到秋叶原啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天接下来在Soft One有DVD的发售活动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空在这里闲聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但时间还早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 再磨蹭就占不到好位子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点 走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代我向她问好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让你久等了 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？春香？不见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她跑去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛….
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只顾找人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 这种地方没有人啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这人山人海里乱跑 太没常识了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我不是故意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 抱歉 是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我在找一个十足像个大小姐的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 和女朋友走散了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友 朋友而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里好希望她做你的女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害羞 别害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才有见过那种女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就在那边的小巷里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你误会了啦 裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,语言又不通 正愁着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在给他们指路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（男1：嗨 小姐 他难道是你的男朋友？）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（春：啊 我们是朋友）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（春：他好像误以为你们是坏人了）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（男2：看来是 喂 小子）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是春香 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 裕人 没告诉你就走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GACHAPON会馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小秋耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭蛋又不贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春香的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不论是看还是摸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 这叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是所谓「初体验」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初 初 字面上虽然没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 很简单的 不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 那我就试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是摇不出想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又重了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 这次我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 春香小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 算了 转扭蛋是要靠运气的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着是去＠home cafe吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对了 还有下一家店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊 打起精神继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店看上去还挺普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人 这菜单好可爱的 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 确实很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 大小姐 想好点什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再等… 咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么了？主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么进门时没注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？春香 春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 你男朋友都等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？为 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 店员们非要我穿穿看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 请不要一直盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我会难为情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 男朋友 这时候应该夸奖一番才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好可爱 我又不是她男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害羞别害羞 来 站紧点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛看这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 萌萌地笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍的好壮烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也蛮开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还拿到了照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 裕人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那么终于到压轴戏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 向着Portable Dream Station Let's Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,售
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完
