Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
